#FILE HANDLING:
        ->file handling is used to create,read,write and modify files.
        ->we use the 'open()' function for file operations.
   #syntax
        variable_name=open("file_name","mode")
   #example
        file=open("name.txt","r")

   ->First of all,want to create a file and fill the file with content whatever may be,then save this file in same folder where you save the programs running(enga program save pannuriyo andha same folder la)

File Modes

Mode	             Meaning
"r"         -     Read file
"w"	         -    Write file (creates new file or overwrites existing content)
"a"	         -   Append data to the file
"x"          -   	Create a new file
"r+"         -   	Read and write

 
     

                            
